{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/spartan_oath_headline.png?t=1738329823\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Last_Spartan_Steam_Page_Top_Leonidas.gif?t=1738329823\" /><br><br>King Leonidas and his valiant Spartan warriors return triumphantly from their campaigns, only to face a dark and horrifying fate. Their victory has awakened an ancient, eldritch force that lays waste to their fleet. As the sole survivor, King Leonidas is left alone, tormented by guilt and madness. Driven by a burning resolve, he must conquer his inner demons and embark on an epic quest to liberate his homeland from the clutches of insanity. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Untitled_design.png?t=1738329823\" /><br>Choose your ally god from a pool of 10+ Greek gods, all offering different active and passive abilities, allowing you to try different builds, play styles and strategies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/download.gif?t=1738329823\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/byod_new.png?t=1738329823\" /><br>Build your own dice to create a custom deck for turn-based battles. Customize your dice to your own strategy, bring out new and unique synergies and combos coupled with each God's unique abilities. Dice faces are rewards for winning each battle encounter, add them to your collection to progress on your roguelike run.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Last_Spartan_Dice_Building_Steam.gif?t=1738329823\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Untitled_design__2_.png?t=1738329823\" /><br>Encounter new random events and face new enemies each playthrough. Choices matter with each encounter, leading to either rewards, blessings, or curses. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Last_Spartan_NPC_More.gif?t=1738329823\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Untitled_design__3_.png?t=1738329823\" /><br>Collect powerful artifacts during encounters, granting permanent stats and abilities for the rest of your run.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/last_spartan_artifacts_gif.gif?t=1738329823\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Untitled_design__4_.png?t=1738329823\" /><br>Your path towards the final battle will be filled with encounters and narrative events, keep your mind sharp and try not to lose your sanity as you defeat and face Lovecraftian horrors.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/Last_Spartan_Walking_Animation_Exploring_Greece_Map_Node_Gameplay_Steam.gif?t=1738329823\" /><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WISHLIST &amp; FOLLOW FOR UPDATES</h2></strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1738329823\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2488270?t=1738329823","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738329823","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488270/4f3a23d5a9b78692b6a703867e5f8b591206ec43/capsule_